snippet.title: Primal Omen Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam Now!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1865710/Primal_Omen/

Explore a lush tropical island overrun by fierce dinosaurs. A third person survival horror experience where you must adapt and survive against these epic beasts. Unearth why dinosaurs roam the earth once more.
